---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact Gotham Web Dev | Request a Free Consultation
description: Contact Gotham Web Dev for a free consultation on web design, SEO, hosting, or AI workflow implementation for your business.
canonical: https://www.gothamwebdev.com/contact.html
pageKey: contact
navRoot: ""
permalink: /contact.html
breadcrumbs:
  - label: Home
    href: index.html
  - label: Contact
---
<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
      <p>Tell us what you need and we will follow up with a practical scope and timeline.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="container cards-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Direct Contact</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong>
          <a href="mailto:{{ business.contact.email }}" title="Email Gotham Web Dev">{{ business.contact.email }}</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Phone:</strong>
          <a href="tel:+1{{ business.contact.phone }}" title="Call Gotham Web Dev">{{ business.contact.phoneDisplay | default(business.contact.phone) }}</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Address:</strong><br />
          {{ business.address.street }}<br />
          {{ business.address.city }}, {{ business.address.state }} {{ business.address.zip }}
        </p>
      </article>

      <form class="card" action="#" method="post" aria-label="Contact form">
        <p><label for="name">Full Name</label><br /><input id="name" name="name" type="text" required /></p>
        <p><label for="email">Email</label><br /><input id="email" name="email" type="email" required /></p>
        <p><label for="service">Service Needed</label><br /><input id="service" name="service" type="text" /></p>
        <p><label for="message">Project Details</label><br /><textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea></p>
        <p><button class="btn" type="submit">Send Request</button></p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
